title: Under the Roof Decorating 5-100200 15 lb Place&Push Canvas Hangers , White
description: Place & Push Canvas Hangers are a quick, easy and a secure way to hang canvas art in drywall. Canvas sits flush against the wall for a professional designer look. Mini level helps hang canvas straight. Visually hang canvas to create beautiful displays. Designed for drywall only. Holds 15 lbs. securely .
